data.description: Discover this charming pool home tucked away off Scenic Highway in Pensacola's beautiful Gulf Coast region. This delightful residence boasts three bedrooms and two bathrooms, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style. As you step inside, you'll find cathedral ceilings in the main living area, creating an inviting atmosphere centered around a cozy brick fireplace. You'll appreciate the combination of tile and wood-look flooring throughout the home. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and features a breakfast nook that leads seamlessly to the formal dining area, making meal preparation and entertaining a breeze. One of the highlights of this home is the sunroom, which provides a picturesque view of the inviting pool/hot tub area and the spacious backyard. Whether enjoying your morning coffee or hosting gatherings, this space will surely be a favorite. The primary bedroom features cathedral ceilings, direct access to the screen back porch, and a few steps to the hot tub waiting for you. You'll also find a well-appointed bathroom and a large walk-in closet, offering convenience and extra storage. This home has one of the largest lots in the Bay Woods Subdivision. Don't miss the opportunity to make this lovely pool home yours! Book your private showing today.
